= Anti Aviary =
The concept of an anti aviary is that it keeps the birds out rather than in. It is designed to protect the plants within from wild birds the area. An example of the type of design envisioned is shown below.

{{attachment:AntiAviaryExample.jpg|Anti Aviary Example using posts and wires|align="middle"}}

== Anti-Aviary Design ==
=== Supporting Structure ===
The primary support for the anti-aviary will be provided by log posts set into the ground at the edges of the tree rows that are under protection. Atop the posts wire will be run

